{"tid":1395904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"修例風波：示威者拉起馬鞍山警署大閘 防暴警到場驅散","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T02:13:53.000Z","uid":56881,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a33c1bfbd16bd4b80837354f7967bf4fa1d87c","tid":1395904,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8B%89%E8%B5%B7%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%98-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3-221821740.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2596%2598-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3-221821740.html&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=dbbe1b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8B%89%E8%B5%B7%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%98-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3-221821740.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WSQHrMZVf0LVUHWxi3M1IA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/15dfcfa0-b4aa-11e9-be77-5be4fb47229f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWSQHrMZVf0LVUHWxi3M1IA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F15dfcfa0-b4aa-11e9-be77-5be4fb47229f&h=baf05c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防暴警察向馬鞍山警署推進。(梁穎福攝)<br />\n<br />\n【04:28】火炭工廈被捕其中一名男疑犯報稱不適，由兩名防暴警押送往醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n【03:05】防暴警驅散馬鞍山警署外示威者，將他們趕至曾璧山中學對開公園，示威者進一步退到西沙路。而警署附近路邊停有多輛違泊私家車，示威者四散後，多名司機返回上址取車，警方懷疑他們跟示威有關，遂搜查車輛，惟並無發現任何違禁品。<br />\n<br />\n【02:50】防暴警察向馬鞍山警署方向前進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.CONKT9_J19C1mq.WiKbkA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/2ed805e0-b4aa-11e9-9716-2695223c66cf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.CONKT9_J19C1mq.WiKbkA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F2ed805e0-b4aa-11e9-9716-2695223c66cf&h=983feaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者衝破馬鞍山警署正門大閘。(吳建明攝)<br />\n<br />\n邊個連鐵閘都拉起埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc36d5c2233e582f53d153d58e7b1a11c4c7154","tid":1395904,"uid":8441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"擺明唔鎖閘裝你彈弓，話你衝擊警署"},{"pid":"259abe6ef7f57273c1c2e9fd31c595b50867bc85","tid":1395904,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功be water"},{"pid":"e89c78f9a2920a83a084ea9b91aae26488a8f62f","tid":1395904,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc36d5c2233e582f53d153d58e7b1a11c4c7154","tid":1395904,"uid":8441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"擺明唔鎖閘裝你彈弓，話你衝擊警署"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"乜黑警講野仲有公信力咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6dd635a2c14f5d04addbc5b7fcb88d7e8c9d2e","tid":1395904,"uid":199640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"正確示範<br />\n無預同佢火拼咪be water囉"},{"pid":"fff267e